/*-

 * ssl_check_for_safari attempts to fingerprint Safari using OS X

 * SecureTransport using the TLS extension block in |hello|.

 *   SNI,

 *   elliptic_curves

        0x00, 0x06,             /* 6 bytes of curve ids */

    


    

    
1341

1342
